2fa","tid":1506555,"uid":165752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f440ba38d888b446eb6aa40c6c9bce29355d134","tid":1506555,"uid":281652,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:05:37.000Z","msg":"唔好簽<br />\n伏嚟呀 <br />\n<br />\nPeople in Hong Kong who hold the British National (Overseas) passport are British; however, the British government is refusing and avoiding giving these Hong Kongers the<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">More details<br />\nThe Chinese government is ignoring the Sino Anglo Agreements signed in 1981. It could be a disaster if we keep ignoring this is happening. Hong Kongers will come in as political refugees. We will need a lot of effort to house them and bad for the British reputations to the International community then.</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:09:53.000Z","msg":"咩問題"},{"pid":"cf2fae29c3a7defce7d9269b07e6f08b632beeff","tid":1506555,"uid":82851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:14:29.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a983f32d1db25b916ab95a08a7a6e4dc046a4a67","tid":1506555,"uid":165752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db3e0d891956aff963b42b960645871f45382b6","tid":1506555,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:31:03.000Z","msg":"BNO平權文宣方向<br />\n不過, 從7月開始, 英國輿論 &ndash; 從每日快報, 衛報, 觀察者, 甚至太陽報紛紛鼓吹<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>英國政府應給予BNO持有者BC身份</ins></strong></span>. 值得一提的是英國智庫Adam Smith Institute在8月15日出了一份名為Doing Our Duty的研究報告, 建議<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">英國政府應將BNO權利擴大至與BC同等</span></ins></strong>, 因為若BNO人成為BC, 這&rdquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>將會促使中國和平地行事</ins></strong></span>&rdquo; (p. 6), 香港人可以&rdquo;在自由的環境下生活, 而中國則失去一整代人,<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"> 英國會得到道德和物質上的勝利</span></ins></strong>&rdquo; (p. 7). 不只如此, <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人&rdquo;人均收入高, 高學歷及具備專業技能, 對英國經濟會有實質益處</span></ins></strong>&rdquo; (p. 8). 最後, <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">英國幫BNO升級可顯示英國&rdquo;並未忘記其角色和放棄原則&rdquo;</span></ins></strong> (p. 9). 這份報告暗示: a. BNO是&rdquo;和平時代&rdquo;的產物. 只要中英間利益衝突, BNO會是英國的招數: 中國領土內突然出現大批BC會<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">使英國有理由介入香港事務</span></ins></strong>, 這也是為什麼當初英國不給港人BC身份, 卻要弄出BNO, 而中國則要強加中國籍給香港人的根本原因 (英國不要收留港人; 中國收港人, 但條件是&rdquo;管得了&rdquo;的港人. 反正要抓人只要說句他是&rdquo;中國人&rdquo;就行) (結論1和3); b. 英國對香港的&rdquo;道義和責任&rdquo;乃建基在利益上, 尤其<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">正值英國脫歐, 香港將可成為英國經濟的救火員</span></ins></strong> (結論2)."},{"pid":"ef7cfd77abed8beb17e48cdf8b609be6af7a98cc","tid":1506555,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"BNO平權文宣方向<br />\n不過, 從7月開始, 英國輿論 &ndash; 從每日快報, 衛報, 觀察者, 甚至太陽報紛紛鼓吹<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>英國政府應給予BNO持有者BC身份</ins></strong></span>. 值得一提的是英國智庫Adam Smith Institute在8月15日出了一份名為Doing Our Duty的研究報告, 建議<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">英國政府應將BNO權利擴大至與BC同等</span></ins></strong>, 因為若BNO人成為BC, 這&rdquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>將會促使中國和平地行事</ins></strong></span>&rdquo; (p. 6), 香港人可以&rdquo;在自由的環境下生活, 而中國則失去一整代人,<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"> 英國會得到道德和物質上的勝利</span></ins></strong>&rdquo; (p. 7). 不只如此, <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人&rdquo;人均收入高, 高學歷及具備專業技能, 對英國經濟會有實質益處</span></ins></strong>&rdquo; (p. 8). 最後, <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">英國幫BNO升級可顯示英國&rdquo;並未忘記其角色和放棄原則&rdquo;</span></ins></strong> (p. 9). 這份報告暗示: a. BNO是&rdquo;和平時代&rdquo;的產物. 只要中英間利益衝突, BNO會是英國的招數: 中國領土內突然出現大批BC會<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">使英國有理由介入香港事務</span></ins></strong>, 這也是為什麼當初英國不給港人BC身份, 卻要弄出BNO, 而中國則要強加中國籍給香港人的根本原因 (英國不要收留港人; 中國收港人, 但條件是&rdquo;管得了&rdquo;的港人. 反正要抓人只要說句他是&rdquo;中國人&rdquo;就